# Google Drive Upload Sessions API - Sync Upload Sessions Data
created: 2019-01-01, last updated: 2026-01-30, [Read more](https://www.apideck.com/integrations/google-drive/upload-sessions)

Sync permissioned upload sessions data with Google Drive through Apideck's unified API.
One integration, instant access to the governed data your team needs.
...
Start syncing Google Drive upload sessions in minutes
```
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/unify'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: process.env.APIDECK_API_KEY,
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'YOUR_CONSUMER_ID'
})
// List upload sessions from Google Drive
const result = await apideck.file-storage.uploadSessions.list({
serviceId: 'google-drive'
})
for await (const page of result) {
console.log(page)
